        <div class="overflow-x-auto [&_pre]:p-4 [&_pre]:!bg-[var(--color-bg-code)] [&_pre]:m-0 [&_code]:font-mono [&_code]:text-sm [&_code]:leading-relaxed" style="max-height: 500px; overflow-y: auto;">
